    FileMaker Server Advanced v12.0.1 *MULTiLANGUAGE* (c) FileMaker Inc.

   Securely host groups of FileMaker Pro  users over a network or  on  the
   web by adding FileMaker Server. It's fast, reliable, easy-to-use server
   software for securely managing your FileMaker Pro databases.

   When using FileMaker Go for iPad  and  iPhone,  connect  to   databases
   hosted  on  FileMaker Server for  instant  access to the  most  current
   information. Any changes you make to your data  while you're on the  go
   are immediately  accessible  to   your    entire    team.   Connect  to
   FileMaker Server   using  a   local   wireless network  or   over   the
   Internet using Wi-Fi or 3G.

   FileMaker Server 12 Advanced       includes   all   the   features   in
   FileMaker Server 12 plus more sharing and  connectivity  options.   Add
   FileMaker Server 12 Advanced   to  FileMaker Pro   and   maximize  your
   database  sharing   capabilities. Or  host  FileMaker Go  databases  on
   FileMaker Served Advanced to share the  latest  information  with  your
   team while you're on the go.

